    {
      "start": 364.95,
      "end": 368.25,
      "text": "And it looked like it was so intelligent."
    },
    {
      "start": 368.49,
      "end": 369.47,
      "text": "맞아요. 똑똑해요."
    },
    {
      "start": 369.55,
      "end": 370.41,
      "text": "If you look in their eyes,"
    },
    {
      "start": 370.41,
      "end": 371.93,
      "text": "it looks like they're thinking"
    },
    {
      "start": 371.93,
      "end": 373.33,
      "text": "and they're loving."
    },
    {
      "start": 373.47,
      "end": 373.81,
      "text": "Wow."
    },
    {
      "start": 373.95,
      "end": 375.81,
      "text": "And they came right up to the glass"
    },
    {
      "start": 375.81,
      "end": 377.61,
      "text": "and were just staring at us."
    },
    {
      "start": 377.87,
      "end": 378.51,
      "text": "진짜요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 378.53,
      "end": 381.11,
      "text": "It was absolutely an incredible experience."
    },
    {
      "start": 381.13,
      "end": 382.67,
      "text": "와, 그 벨루가들도"
    },
    {
      "start": 382.67,
      "end": 384.23,
      "text": "우리 크쌤을 알아봤나봐요."
    },
    {
      "start": 384.63,
      "end": 385.47,
      "text": "아, 그런가요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 386.71,
      "end": 387.81,
      "text": "Oh, yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 387.97,
      "end": 389.49,
      "text": "네, 근데 이번에 애니메이션의"
    },
    {
