    },
    {
      "start": 484.8,
      "end": 486.6,
      "text": "Well, snails, they're sneak snails."
    },
    {
      "start": 486.76,
      "end": 488.82,
      "text": "They live in the ocean, in the water."
    },
    {
      "start": 489.02,
      "end": 492.02,
      "text": "But here, I think it's more of an insult."
    },
    {
      "start": 492.56,
      "end": 494.08,
      "text": "Krusty old snail."
    },
    {
      "start": 494.4,
      "end": 495.98,
      "text": "Snails are really slow."
    },
    {
      "start": 496.22,
      "end": 497.14,
      "text": "아, 무서운."
    },
    {
      "start": 497.16,
      "end": 498.78,
      "text": "And a harabuji snail is even slower."
    },
    {
      "start": 499.46,
      "end": 499.7,
      "text": "그러니까."
    },
    {
      "start": 500.04,
      "end": 500.64,
      "text": "아, 그래요."
    },
    {
      "start": 500.72,
      "end": 505.16,
